                },
                "text": "The pudding has a +9 counteract modifier. You also become quickened for 1 round. While taking the additional action from being quickened, you scream, as a result of both the flavor and the mandrake paste's properties. You can use the additional action to Step, Stride, Strike, or Demoralize . If you choose to Demoralize, you gain a +2 item bonus to the Intimidation check.",
